  "title": "Operations Analyst (MIS & Reporting) (Banking)",
  "description": "<ul><li><p>Collaborate closely with internal partners and relevant departments for data extraction, MIS, audits, and regulatory data requests.</p></li></ul><p><ul><li>Ensure the timely submission of regulatory reports for OTC Derivative products to the relevant regulatory bodies.</li><li>Manage the setup of market rules and oversee trade approvals within the Pre-trade Validation queue.<br /><br />Ensure full compliance with all applicable laws, regulations, and internal policies.</li><li><p>Partner with relevant teams to fulfill all regulatory requirements.</p></li><li>Oversee data extraction to ensure information is provided on a \"need-to-know\" basis, ensuring appropriate approvals and checks and balances are in place.<br /><br />To apply online please use the 'apply' function. </li><li> <strong>(EA: 94C3609/ R24124496)</strong></li></ul></p>",
